** Reporting bugs **

Bugs should be sent to the AssetGuard mailling list
(https://groups.google.com/forum/#!forum/assetguard). Please, make sure to include
the following information:

-Output of "ASSETGUARD_HOME/bin/assetguard-control info"
-Content of ASSETGUARD_HOME/etc/<assetguard configuration file>
-Content of ASSETGUARD_HOME/logs/<assetguard log file>
-Operating system name/version (uname -a if Unix)
-Any other relevant information.


If you prefer to contact us privately or want to report a
security issue, send an e-mail to AssetGuard (support@assetguard.com).
